ement, Year and Life Cycles, Biography, Medical Cycles - consider a wide range of evidence and of recent scholarship, while highlighting the contribution of medical texts.  aIssued also in print.  afunded by Einstein Center Chronoi  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mai 2023) 4aAntike. 4aGalenus. 4aZeit. 4aZeitwahrnehmung. 7aRELIGION / Ancient.2bisacsh  aGalen.  atime awareness.  atime in antiquity.  atime pereception.2 aEinstein Center Chronoiefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2022 Part 1z978311076682008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig.Stud., Jewish Stud. 2022 Englishz978311099454408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig.Stud., Jewish Stud. 2022z9783110994537oZDB-23-DGF0 cEPUBz97831107524960 cprintz978311075192540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110752397zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110752397zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110752397/original  a978-3-11-076682-0 DG Plus DeG Package 2022 Part 1b2022  a978-3-11-099389-9 EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-099454-4 EBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig.Stud., Jewish Stud. 2022 Englishb2022  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGFb2022  aZDB-23-DGGb2022  aZDB-23-GOA